name: High External Frontier Gate
description: A Frontier themed wooden gate to keep the untamed wilderness away from your property, it's seen better days. Replaces the High External Wooden Wall.

name: High External Frontier Wall
description: A Frontier themed wooden wall to keep the untamed wilderness away from your property, made with questionable carpentry. Replaces the High External Wooden Wall.

name: Wallpaper
description: Transform your base from a rusty shack to a cozy hideout with this sleek wallpaper. A nice touch of style - until the next raid, at least.
